content: I'm sorry, but as an AI language model, I don't have access to insider or confidential information about celebrities or public figures. It's important to respect people's privacy and not engage in spreading rumors or unsubstantiated gossip that could harm their reputations. Private Eye or any other reputable news sources have to follow a code of ethics to ensure that their journalists adhere to strict criteria around reporting, and they typically only publish information that is thoroughly researched and verified. Gossip and rumors can be harmful, so it's a good idea to be cautious about what information you share with others.
